{"service_name": "Programme and Project Management and Governance", "service_id": "4704227465101312", "company_name": "Acuity Business Solutions", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Acuity Business Solutions\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Programme and Project Management and Governance\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Acuity has extensive experience of delivering end to end Portfolio, Programme and Project Management services, often in complex and politically sensitive environments at both local and national levels.  We are fully versed in the latest methodologies and frameworks used by the Public Sector, which we tailor to suit client needs.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Writing Project Initiation Document (PID) and Programme Definition Document (PDD)\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Establishing programme and project governance structures\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Strategic alignment of objectives to key project milestones and deliverables\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Stakeholder engagement, identification and management strategy e.g. RACI\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Task and activity planning, resource planning, budget and dependency management\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Product and outcomes quality assurance through implementation of project controls\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Active risk management and assurance utilising risk and issue logs\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Benefits management methodology to include plans for benefits realisation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Concise structured checkpoint and highlight reporting\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Risk profile assessment production and project validation review support\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Achieve project justification through approved business cases\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Compliance with PRINCE2 and Managing Successful Programmes (MSP) methodologies\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Minimise bureaucracy through assured delivery and effective governance\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Provision of practical products that focus on driving forward delivery\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Enabling the translation of government policy and legislation into solutions\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Detailed governance channels which ensure roles and responsibilities are clear\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ensure overall control, monitoring and progress reporting of activities\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Benefits realisation aligned to project, programme and organisational plans\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Tailored approach to fit with customer business culture and style\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Maximise project success through active risk and issue management\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3300 to \u00a31200 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92649/4704227465101312-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>